{n}Nok-Nok follows your gesture, and as he turns...
...but already unsteady, he twists and falls again, collapsing to the ground – the drumming falls awkwardly silent with a few gasps, then laughing from the goblins.
To his credit, Nok-Nok picks himself up and dusts himself off, then the drumming resumes. He's giving a half-smile, as if he's not certain of his own success.{/n}
